org.hibernate.reactive.session

Interface ReactiveQueryExecutor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ReactiveConnectionSupplier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ReactiveSession, ReactiveStatelessSession

    public interface ReactiveQueryExecutor
extends ReactiveConnectionSupplier
    Executes queries in a non-blocking fashion. An internal contract between the NativeQueryImplementors and stateless and stateful reactive sessions.
    See Also:
    SharedSessionContractImplementor
